microsoft.hawaii.hawaiiClientLibraryBase.DataContract

Class ServiceResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • microsoft.hawaii.hawaiiClientLibraryBase.DataContract.ServiceResult
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DeleteResult, EndpointResult, GetByKeyResult, GetByKeysResult, GetLanguagesForSpeakResponse, GetLanguagesForTranslateResponse, GetResult, GroupResult, MessageResult, NameRegistrationResult, OcrServiceResult, PredictLocationResult, SetResult, SpeakResponse, SpeechServiceResult, TranslateResponse

    public abstract class ServiceResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for all Hawaii service result classes. Various Hawaii service result classes will represent the result corresponding to different type of Hawaii service calls. This class contains functionality common to all Hawaii service result classes.
